a:3:{s:11:"notes_total";i:1;s:11:"notes_ctree";a:1:{i:0;a:32:{s:2:"id";i:70;s:5:"title";s:64:"Follow Up Boss brings voice prompts to Smart Messages on mobile";s:4:"href";s:93:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/all/follow-up-boss-brings-voice-prompts-to-smart-messages-on-mobile/";s:13:"href-original";s:93:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/all/follow-up-boss-brings-voice-prompts-to-smart-messages-on-mobile/";s:4:"time";a:2:{i:0;i:1769591170;i:1;a:2:{s:6:"offset";i:18000;s:6:"is_dst";b:0;}}s:13:"last-modified";a:2:{i:0;i:1769591163;i:1;a:2:{s:6:"offset";i:18000;s:6:"is_dst";b:0;}}s:4:"text";s:1115:"<p>Follow Up Boss updated its mobile app to let users create Smart Messages using voice input. Instead of typing a custom prompt, users can speak it and generate an AI draft for a text or email.</p>
<h3>What’s new</h3>
<ul>
<li>Voice-to-prompt input for Smart Messages on mobile</li>
<li>Generates AI drafts for texts and emails</li>
<li>Uses the full lead timeline and activity for context</li>
<li>Works on iOS and Android</li>
<li>Drafts are reviewable/editable before sending</li>
</ul>
<h3>How it works</h3>
<ol start="1">
<li>Start a text or email on mobile</li>
<li>Choose the custom prompt Smart Message option</li>
<li>Tap the microphone</li>
<li>Speak your prompt</li>
<li>Review/edit the generated message, then send</li>
</ol>
<h3>Rollout</h3>
<p>The feature is rolling out via mobile app updates over the next week (auto-update or update manually).</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://updates.followupboss.com/en/use-your-voice-to-create-custom-smart-messages-on-mobile">https://updates.followupboss.com/en/use-your-voice-to-create-custom-smart-messages-on-mobile</a></p>
